can't get agro fast enough nowadays when an add's hitting on a caster
or such.&nbsp; I try (chain casting incapacitate or such) and usually don't
get anywhere within 8-10 seconds, then a war walks over and 1 click
taunts it off casually.<br>
<br>
We used to have poison DoTs as a good agro tool... those were nerfed
into worthlessness with the poison-agro change a while back.&nbsp; Our
remaining tools are mediocre at best for gaining agro.<br>
<br>
There's that taunt change this patch too, so war/pal/shd/rng get even
further boosts to their ability to snatch agro.&nbsp; Beastlords are falling
behind in yet another area.<br>
