<DIV>The removed the cooldown from a failed taunt.&nbsp; So if taunt fails can immediately try again instead of waiting for the skill to reset.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I used to love the fact that we could gain quick agro.&nbsp; It allowed us to save priests and casters.&nbsp; Now no snap agro and in the time it takes incap or whatever is your favorite way to get agro to work the person your saving is dead.&nbsp; I honestly have beat on mobs till they are at 50% before getting agro from a enchanter that cast slow before I did while the cleric is chain healing him.&nbsp; Kinda sad when you compare it to how the old poison DoTs used to work.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
