		" 
			>
			<DIV></DIV>
<P>Taunt cap was raised for Rangers also, just not as high 200max.</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>Little things Ive done to reduce my agro on raids and greatly increase my survivability:</P>
<P>-Wait a few seconds after assist has been called to allow others to start building agro first so as to be higher on the hate list.</P>
<P>-Don't open up with nukes, let the mob get beat down a little bit first. Generally wait until ~90% for first nukes now.</P>
<P>-Swapped in life tap augs. They seem to generate less agro then dd augs and help survivablility from the heals.</P>
<P>-Turn pet taunt off. This should not affect our agro since pet agro is suppose to be separate from ours but I'm suspicious....</P>
<P>-Don't use dots, I know they lowered the agro on these but they still generate some and generally don't land anyway.</P>	
